{"tid":1023354,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【火辣！】前意大利女球證成《花花公子》模特兒","createTime":"2019-02-15T16:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T10:05:40.000Z","uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"544fe65c221e09be0e0da6648b702b4823485ce0","tid":1023354,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T16:44:38.000Z","msg":"平日在足球場上奔馳的，除了雙方廿二名球員外，還有滿場飛的球證，甚至他們獲得的焦點不會較場上的球員少，如果遇到前意大利女球證 Claudia Romani 執法，相信不少球迷都會把目光投射到這位美女球證身上。<br />\n早前這位美女球證為意大利版《花花公子》拍攝情人節照片，相中的她換上一身火辣紅色的性感內衣，並在一張掛滿紅色心心的大床上，擺出各式各樣性感撩人的姿勢，非常誘人。<br />\n可惜球迷現時已經沒有機會再看到 Claudia Romani 執法，因為這位 AC 米蘭球迷，兼名宿恩沙基的前女友已經轉行，擔任全職模特兒，雖然她表示十分享受做球證的機會，但相信短期內都不會再參與球證的工作了"},{"pid":"d6d7ff095989cd118e991f7fb5348313bc73fc98","tid":1023354,"uid":221490,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T16:46:16.000Z","msg":"伯母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8eefe811333f11db58905f7f59be8b9cd515405","tid":1023354,"uid":45830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:25:52.000Z","msg":"準備好未？"},{"pid":"577906da2cd20fa87437ee8e7d366a0e4293a74b","tid":1023354,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:41:50.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"34f3a89565c7cdb4ad7d8c527aeebca8374d46ff","tid":1023354,"uid":223525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T18:07:23.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"42eef8d530d51594210fab16dee5911826afe175","tid":1023354,"uid":56351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T18:08:04.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"8d3ed0f2a42d79bc9cf72fd5b0590640d40834d2","tid":1023354,"uid":66178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T23:43:14.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"eb52c16a7464b51a18f9f5ff9370ff32ebb23737","tid":1023354,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T23:48:28.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"1881f3073a80111c4aed2c1aedaae587108020c1","tid":1023354,"u